  <brief_title>Public Health Emergency: SOLIDARITY TRIAL Philippines</brief_title>
  <official_title>An International Randomized Trial of Additional Treatments for COVID-19 in Hospitalized Patients Who Are All Receiving the Local Standard of Care Philippines</official_title>
