  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is an adaptive, randomized, open-label, controlled clinical trial utilizing an&#xD;
      adaptive design to compare effects of repurposed drugs with local standard of care alone on&#xD;
      major inpatient hospital outcomes. This is performed worldwide in collaboration with WHO.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
